ROCKETS POKER ROOM Rockets poker room is India’s largest poker room that offers fulltime high grade poker action to quench any and all poker desires that you might have. Get your poker face on and barge into our adrenaline pumping card rooms;which also happen to be the most colossal and active in the country; to play the belle of poker Texas No limit hold’em/Pot limit omaha. We have sparkling deepstack tables with a wide array and personalities of players. We offer some of the biggest poker room games in the country; right in the bosom of bangalore; with well trained dealers to cater to all of your card’y’ needs and queries. Choose the table which comforts your bankroll and playing style. We are open all days of the week, so be ready for some heart racing poker action whenever you decide to drop by. We ensure you the most deeply rewarding and premium tournaments weekly althroughout the year for players of all stack sizes. Irrespective of the depth of your pocket be sure to find yourself a welcoming spot at our action heavy board.
See you at the tables!
